						<p>[Sadāsivarāya]—(Undated).</p>						

						<p>This undated epigraph records the remission of marriage-tax in <hi rend="bold">Huligere-nāḍu,</hi> by the king at the instance of Liṁgiseṭṭi. This may be assigned to the reign of Sādās11ivarāya of the Vijayanagara empire.</p>						

